article.headline: DePaul takes down Chicago State 70-58
article.description: — Elijah Fisher's 16 points helped DePaul defeat Chicago State 70-58 on Saturday night.
article.story: CHICAGO -- — Elijah Fisher's 16 points helped DePaul defeat Chicago State 70-58 on Saturday night. Fisher had seven rebounds for the Blue Demons (3-9). K.T. Raimey scored 15 points and added five rebounds. Da'Sean Nelson had 11 points and finished 5 of 9 from the floor. The Cougars (7-12) were led in scoring by Wesley Cardet Jr., who finished with 18 points. Brent Davis added 15 points for Chicago State. Jahsean Corbett also had 11 points and seven rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
